    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CCU is a fusion product for SGM which will use TC387 as SCC and QAM8775 as SOC"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Important part of this fusion is the complete use of SAIL domain for ADAS processing"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Block diagram"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Overall Block diagram can be found in below path"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "16_CCU - All Documents (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Our focus is on Autosar domain in SCC and SAIL domain"
    },
